desc_long								关于这款游戏							Modbox is a VR physics sandbox game for the HTC Vive. Create your own Holodeck experience to play with and to share with othersCreate Rube Goldberg style large room scale creations with the Vive’s precise controllersShare your work on Steam workshop ingame, or try out others onlineConstruct with primitives by just touching them together. Add in hinge joints, ropes, propellers, rockets, piston, balloons. Then control them by wiring them together with throttles and levers.Pick up and play with toys to interact with the world - including baseball bats, basketballs, crossbows, pistols, chainsaws...						
